title: Winning numbers drawn in 'Pick 3' game
maintext:
OKLAHOMA CITY (AP) _ The winning numbers in Monday evening’s drawing of the Oklahoma Lottery’s “Pick 3” game were:
8-4-7
(eight, four, seven)
